<span id="freeTextContainer2104072072673728984">Fascinating. I love Michael Pollan&apos;s work. I have to say, his account made me want to try psilocybin as part of my research . I&apos;m not sure how one goes about doing that. If you have any suggestions, email me.</span>
  <span id="freeText2104072072673728984" style="display:none">Fascinating. I love Michael Pollan's work. I have to say, his account made me want to try psilocybin as part of my research . I'm not sure how one goes about doing that. If you have any suggestions, email me.</span>
